description:
Welcome to the newly reduced 309 Church Street—your urban oasis in the heart of Nashville.

Perched just steps from Printer’s Alley and Broadway’s legendary Honky Tonks, this 2-bedroom, 1.5-bath condo perfectly blends historic character with modern style.

Entertain in the open-concept living space, featuring soaring ceilings and direct access to an expansive private terrace—ideal for skyline cocktails, weekend brunches, or quiet mornings overlooking Printer’s Alley and the Cumberland River.

Two rare, privately gated parking spaces eliminate the hassle of downtown parking—an unbeatable perk that makes city living effortless.

Freshly painted, move-in ready, and complete with all appliances, this home offers a polished mix of comfort and cool. Whether you’re seeking a full-time residence or the ultimate downtown retreat, 309 Church delivers Nashville living at its best.

Don’t miss your chance to own a piece of Music City magic—schedule your showing today!
